wow the quality of the character models is absolutely insane. some of the shots look so realistic. riot never fails to impress artistically every single time..

I’m not quite sure how to put into words the fight with kindred. Particularly when trynd slashes through lamb’s bow. Obviously trynd cannot kill lamb because kindred is a primordial entity, arguably the strongest of any of them (the others being things like fiddlesticks the entity of fear) she is literally a god. But the moment she “dodges” is unnatural. It’s almost as though the world bent for a moment to ensure trynd’s blade wouldn’t touch lamb. His sword slows down, lamb moves in a fraction of a second with no real effort and then simply tilts her head.

It’s also an incredible visual to see what a struggle on the verge of death is like. Wolf’s relentless assault and lamb’s arrows combined very quickly remind you that from a lore perspective kindred is the absolute last thing you want to tango with

처음 장면 : 케일, 모르가나가 아트록스 상대하지만 둘이서 역부족.

모르가나는 검을 다시 잡지 않고 금지된 타락마법(?)으로 착지한 아트록스한테 속박[R]을 걸고 아트록스가 부수려하자 힘을 더 개방하면서(눈가의 검은 무늬가 더 펼쳐짐) 저지.

케일은 금지된 마법을 쓰는 모르가나를 못마땅하게 여기면서도 앞의 아트록스를 잡는게 우선이니 언니인 모르가나가 떨어뜨린 검을 잡고(쌍검) 승천하여(날개가 11렙 케일마냥 빛남) 아트록스에게 화염파를 날림.(스텍 안쌓아도 바로 화염파가 나오는 16렙 케일)



중간 장면 : 시정잡배가 소녀 잡으려고 다가옴.

삿갓 쓴 영감님이 그 사이를 막음.

대나무 봉으로 뚜쉬따쉬(이때까진 잭스인가..? 싶었음)

러브샷으로 영감님과 시정잡배 둘 다 밀려나고 영감님은 무기로 쓰던 대나무 봉이 부숴짐.

앞서 밀려나며 상대가 떨어뜨린 칼을 잡고 삿갓을 벗음.

짜잔 그 영감님은 사실 늙은 야스오였답니다.

바람술사답게 칼에 바람의 힘을 깃들여 넣고 반대손에도 바람의 힘을 꺼냄.

시정잡배들 쫄아서 런.

화살이 날라오는데 야스오가 바람장벽을 켜서 막음.[W]

접근하면서 질풍검[W]

그리고 이어서 강철 폭풍[Q]



마지막 장면 : 트린다미어가 누워있음.

죽음을 감지하고 킨드레드(양과 늑대)가 목숨을 걷으러 접근함.

트린은 불사의 분노[R]을 써서 발악함.

늑대가 트린과 근접전을 하며 시선을 끌고 양은 조용히 트린의 숨통을 끊으려 활 시위를 당김.

그런데 갑자기 뒤에서 많이 본 화살 두개가 날아옴.

트린도 놀라는데 사실 이 두 화살은 뒤에 트린을 지나 그를 노리던 적 병사에게 적중함.

애쉬 등장.

트린은 애쉬를 보자마자 궁 지속시간 끝났는지 눈이 다시 벽안으로 돌아옴.

애쉬가 트린에게 접근하자 죽음의 위기에 벗어난건지 킨드레드가 사라져있음.

애쉬나 하늘 위로 매를 날림.[E]

I see league really trying to reach out to a wider audience at the moment. The new character shown a little while ago that is like Spiro the dragon but if aimed towards a much younger market really had me almost give up hope on the franchise, it didn’t seem to fit even the more cute side of league, it just seemed like one made for the kids.

The new trailer however went in completely the opposite direction, it had very respectful masculine vibes, like a more polished, more tasteful (which I feel bad saying because it was an iconic cult classic and a masterpiece for its time) version of something like the OG Heavy Metal the movie, as well as a nod to old fashioned Samurai movies, OG Berserk, historical Valkyries, etc. It’s been a long time since common media has shown something masculine in a respectable, tasteful way and it almost brought a tear to my eye like it touched a part of my soul. Plus as l mentioned earlier with Kindred being the overarching theme of the trailer it was destined to be a hit! ❤❤❤❤❤❤

Siedem dni minęło od kiedy opuściliśmy port Enroth. Niewolnicy, których uwolniliśmy podczas potyczki z flotą Regan mówią o dziwnych pogłoskach dochodzących z Erathii. Podejrzewam, że ich opowieści mogą mieć w sobie ziarno prawdy. Na razie jednak muszę na własne oczy zobaczyć co wydarzyło się w królestwie mego ojca.
Fale oceanu pochowały wielu z tych, którzy polegli na jego brzegu ale dymiące ruiny Cloudfire powitały nas widokiem śmierci i zniszczenia. Nikt nie przeżył, pobojowisko powiedziało mi jednak wystarczająco wiele o rozegranej tu bitwie. Pomimo ogromu zniszczeń obecność minotaurów na polu bitwy sugerowała napad złaknionej łupów bandy ale oddziały, które dokonały takiego zniszczenia musiały być dobrze wyćwiczone i dowodzone silną ręką.
Winnymi pogromu musieli być władcy podziemi. Widać iż garnizon zamku spodziewał się ataku a pomimo tego został bezlitośnie wybity do ostatniego żołnierza. Wszystkie popełnione tu okrucieństwa napełniły moje serce gniewem. Sztandar Erathii musi wzbudzać respekt i strach wrogów, nikt nie może go bezkarnie poniewierać. Myślę o moim ukochanym Rolandzie i synu Nikolaju. Na jak długo będę zmuszona ich opuścić. Mój obowiązek jest jednak oczywisty. Królestwo mego ojca musi przetrwać. Erathia nigdy nie zostanie rzucona na kolana.

Kindred es la muerte?

No, kindred es la representación previa a la muerte. La muerte como tal es otro ser que llega cuando kindred determina como muere un ser (violento o piadoso)

Trynda ataca a la oveja pero no al lobo, del lobo solo se defiende:

-la oveja es la muerte por piedad o por enfermedad es decir la muerte natural. Recordemos que trynda está en el suelo en la cinemática, no sabemos cuánto tiempo lleva ahí, puede que se estuviera desangrando o tuviera una herida profunda en un órgano. La oveja dispara esperando darle fin a su vida pero trynda la ataca.

Porque el arco de La oveja se rompe?
